        "start": "2014-10-16 04:22:08-07:00",
        "text": "Putting one discuss here rather than one on each of the other docs. We can fix that as appropriate after we chat.\u00a0 Where are the MTI signature and mac algs for these specified? If those can be tracked back via the SAML and jose docs that's fine, but I'm not sure if they are.",
